@model List<Location>
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Locations";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="jumbotron">Favorite Locations</h1>
    <p class="content">This Page is to showcase a compilation of Logan's Favorite Locations.</p>

	With my passion in photography, I have always enjoyed visiting new places.
	There are so many places I would like to visit as soon as I get the chance.
	
	Listed here is a ranked table of my favorite locations to take photos at, along with a description of what makes each location special.

    <div class="content">
		<pre class="divider" style="font-size:5px; font-weight: bold;"> 
